data.title: Watch Josh Homme Reunite With Eagles Of Death Metal Onstage
data.meta_description: Eagles Of Death Metal co-founder Josh Homme has made a rare live appearance with the band at a show in Paris this week, and footage of the Queens Of The Stone Age frontman taking up drumming duties has made its way online.
